A pastebin for things that I want to share that aren't big enough for their own project.

* barclays.rb - screenscrape Barclays online banking for account balances. Uses the .mobi site that has a no-PinSentry no-interaction route.
* podcast.rb - scan a directory for MP3 files and make an RSS 2.0 podcast file that points to them. Useful for a directory of get_iplayer radio MP3s.
